FBIS4-40499 "drsov117_r_94002" FBIS-SOV-94-117 Daily Report 16 Jun 1994 Azerbaijan Armenian Offer for Border Security, Trade Rejected Armenian Offer for Border Security, Trade Rejected NC1606193194 Baku Azerbaycan Radio Televiziyasi Television Network in Azeri 1600 GMT 16 Jun 94 NC1606193194 Baku Azerbaycan Radio Televiziyasi Television Network Azeri BFN [Text] A meeting took place on Sadarak Rayon's border on 14 June between Namik Gasanov, chairman of Nakhichevan Autonomous Republic Supreme Mejlis, and two representatives of the Armenian Republic: Shakhnazaryan, the Armenian president's plenipotentiary representative; and Arutyunyan, chief border guards commissar. An agreement was reached during the two-hour-long meeting to maintain peace on the border. It is being stated in connection with the Armenian side's proposal to open a joint trade center on the border that this is not possible between countries at war and when a part of our territory is under occupation.
